       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. DASHBPGM.

       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       INPUT-OUTPUT SECTION.
       FILE-CONTROL.

           SELECT LOAN-FILE ASSIGN TO LOANIN
               ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
               ACCESS MODE IS SEQUENTIAL
               RECORD KEY IS LOAN-ID
               FILE STATUS IS FS1.

           SELECT DELQ-FILE ASSIGN TO DELQIN
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL
               FILE STATUS IS FS2.

           SELECT DISP-FILE ASSIGN TO DISPIN
               ORGANIZATION IS INDEXED
               ACCESS MODE IS SEQUENTIAL
               RECORD KEY IS DISPUTE-ID
               FILE STATUS IS FS3.

           SELECT NEWU-FILE ASSIGN TO NEWUIN
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL
               FILE STATUS IS FS4.

           SELECT TRAN-FILE ASSIGN TO TRANIN
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL
               FILE STATUS IS FS6.

           SELECT OUT-FILE ASSIGN TO DASHOUT
               ORGANIZATION IS SEQUENTIAL
               FILE STATUS IS FS5.

       DATA DIVISION.
       FILE SECTION.

       FD  LOAN-FILE.
       01  LOAN-REC.
           05 LOAN-ID         PIC X(6).
           05 CUST-ID         PIC 9(5).
           05 SANC-AMT        PIC 9(6).
           05 EMI-START       PIC X(10).
           05 EMI-END         PIC X(10).
           05 INTEREST        PIC 9(2).
           05 EMI-AMT         PIC 9(6).
           05 GRACE-DAYS      PIC 9(2).
           05 PENALTY-AMT     PIC 9(3).
           05 PAY-MODE        PIC X(3).
           05 PROC-DATE       PIC X(10).
           05 TOTAL-PAID      PIC 9(6).
           05 NEXT-DUE        PIC 9(6).
           05 STATUS1         PIC X(6).
           05 TENURE          PIC 9(3).
           05 OVERDUE-AMT     PIC 9(6).
           05 NO-OF-EMI       PIC 9(3).
           05 FORECLOSURE     PIC 9(6).
           05 DUE-DAYS        PIC 9(3).
           05 DUE-AMT         PIC 9(6).
           05 RISK-SCORE      PIC 99.

       FD  DELQ-FILE
           RECORDING MODE IS F.
       01  DELQ-REC          PIC X(80).

       FD  DISP-FILE.
       01  DISP-REC.
           05 DISPUTE-ID     PIC X(11).
           05 DISP-CUST-ID   PIC X(5).
           05 DISP-LOAN-ID   PIC X(6).
           05 DATE1          PIC X(10).
           05 D-AMT          PIC 9(6).
           05 D-TYPE         PIC 9.
           05 RESPONSE       PIC X(20).
           05 REST           PIC X(21).

       FD  NEWU-FILE
           RECORDING MODE IS F.
       01  NEWU-REC          PIC X(150).

       FD  TRAN-FILE
           RECORDING MODE IS F.
       01  TRAN-REC.
           05 TF-TRAN-ID     PIC X(11).
           05 TF-LOAN-ID     PIC X(06).
           05 TF-CUST-ID     PIC X(05).
           05 TF-NAME        PIC X(20).
           05 TF-STATUS      PIC X(08).
           05 TF-ACT-AMT     PIC 9(04)V99.
           05 TF-PAID-AMT    PIC 9(04)V99.
           05 TF-TYPE        PIC X(01).
           05 TF-DATE        PIC X(10).
           05 FILLER         PIC X(7).

       FD  OUT-FILE
           RECORDING MODE IS F.
       01  DASH-REC.
           05 D-ACTIVE        PIC Z(5).
           05 FILLER          PIC X(1).
           05 D-OVERDUE       PIC Z(5).
           05 FILLER          PIC X(1).
           05 D-DISPUTE       PIC Z(5).
           05 FILLER          PIC X(1).
           05 D-NEWUSER       PIC Z(5).
           05 FILLER          PIC X(1).
           05 D-COLLECTION    PIC 9(7).99.
           05 FILLER          PIC X(46).

       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.

       01  WS-EOF1           PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01  WS-EOF2           PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01  WS-EOF3           PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01  WS-EOF4           PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       01 WS-EOF5            PIC X VALUE 'N'.

       01  FS1               PIC XX.
       01  FS2               PIC XX.
       01  FS3               PIC XX.
       01  FS4               PIC XX.
       01  FS5               PIC XX.
       01  FS6               PIC XX.

       01  WS-ACTIVE-COUNT   PIC 9(6) VALUE 0.
       01  WS-OVERDUE-COUNT  PIC 9(6) VALUE 0.
       01  WS-DISPUTE-COUNT  PIC 9(6) VALUE 0.
       01  WS-NEWUSER-COUNT  PIC 9(6) VALUE 0.
       01  WS-TOTAL-COLL     PIC 9(9) VALUE 0.
       01  TOTAL-COLL        PIC Z(7)9.99.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.

       MAIN-PARA.

           OPEN INPUT LOAN-FILE
           OPEN INPUT TRAN-FILE
                INPUT DELQ-FILE
                INPUT DISP-FILE
                INPUT NEWU-FILE
                OUTPUT OUT-FILE.

           DISPLAY 'FS1=' FS1
           DISPLAY 'FS2=' FS2
           DISPLAY 'FS3=' FS3
           DISPLAY 'FS4=' FS4
           DISPLAY 'FS5=' FS5
           DISPLAY 'FS6=' FS6

      ** ---- LOAN FILE (KSDS) ----
           MOVE LOW-VALUES TO LOAN-ID

           START LOAN-FILE KEY >= LOAN-ID
               INVALID KEY
                   MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF1
           END-START

           PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF1 = 'Y'
               READ LOAN-FILE NEXT RECORD
                   AT END
                       MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF1
                   NOT AT END
                       IF STATUS1 = 'ACTIVE'
                           ADD 1 TO WS-ACTIVE-COUNT
                       END-IF
               END-READ
           END-PERFORM

      ***---- DELQ FILE (SEQUENTIAL) ----
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF2 = 'Y'
               READ DELQ-FILE
                   AT END
                       MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF2
                   NOT AT END
                       ADD 1 TO WS-OVERDUE-COUNT
               END-READ
           END-PERFORM

      ** ---- DISPUTE FILE (KSDS) ----
           MOVE LOW-VALUES TO DISPUTE-ID

           START DISP-FILE KEY >= DISPUTE-ID
               INVALID KEY
                   MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF3
           END-START

           PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF3 = 'Y'
               READ DISP-FILE NEXT RECORD
                   AT END
                       MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF3
                   NOT AT END
                       ADD 1 TO WS-DISPUTE-COUNT
               END-READ
           END-PERFORM

      ** ---- NEW USER FILE (SEQUENTIAL) ----
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF4 = 'Y'
               READ NEWU-FILE
                   AT END
                       MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF4
                   NOT AT END
                       IF NEWU-REC(1:6) IS NUMERIC
                        ADD 1 TO WS-NEWUSER-COUNT
                       END-IF
               END-READ
           END-PERFORM
      *------ COLECTION.
           PERFORM UNTIL WS-EOF5 = 'Y'
               READ TRAN-FILE
                   AT END
                       MOVE 'Y' TO WS-EOF5
                   NOT AT END
                       IF TF-PAID-AMT > 0
                          ADD TF-PAID-AMT TO WS-TOTAL-COLL
                       END-IF
               END-READ
           END-PERFORM.
           MOVE WS-TOTAL-COLL TO TOTAL-COLL
      ** ---- WRITE OUTPUT ----
           MOVE WS-ACTIVE-COUNT   TO D-ACTIVE
           MOVE WS-OVERDUE-COUNT  TO D-OVERDUE
           MOVE WS-DISPUTE-COUNT  TO D-DISPUTE
           MOVE WS-NEWUSER-COUNT  TO D-NEWUSER
           MOVE TOTAL-COLL        TO D-COLLECTION

           WRITE DASH-REC

           DISPLAY 'ACTIVE  :' WS-ACTIVE-COUNT
           DISPLAY 'OVERDUE :' WS-OVERDUE-COUNT
           DISPLAY 'DISPUTE :' WS-DISPUTE-COUNT
           DISPLAY 'NEWUSER :' WS-NEWUSER-COUNT

           CLOSE LOAN-FILE
           CLOSE TRAN-FILE
                 DELQ-FILE
                 DISP-FILE
                 NEWU-FILE
                 OUT-FILE

           STOP RUN.
